shit: 2:22: warning: read without -r mangles a backslash in the input, add -r to read the line literally.
     2 |  printf 'a b c\n' | { read first rest; echo "first=$first rest=$rest"; }
       |                       ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ here.
